    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612740/extras/46e577005be03268bf8f3c98a4425b3b.avif?t=1599719548\" width=616 height=213 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612740/extras/7d562037f51ce184b8c86c105d7c8552.avif?t=1599719548\" width=616 height=76 /></span><br><br><strong>Bokida - Heartfelt Reunion</strong>的故事发生在一个处于沉睡中，看似单色调的光世界，随着探索你会一点一点窥知它的壮美。探索充满趣味的周遭环境，感受自由的体验。在旅途中，运用你的能力，让长久分离的两个行星再会。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏内容</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在暗藏许多乐趣的残酷环境中自由探索<br></li><li>改造你周遭的世界，建造和改造大量建筑<br></li><li>解决谜题来彻底改变景观<br></li><li>在这个充满谜团的有趣世界中享受放松愉悦的体验</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612740/extras/10f1576d9fa296ec5c49eec89034edfb.poster.avif?t=1599719548\" width=616 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612740/extras/10f1576d9fa296ec5c49eec89034edfb.webm?t=1599719548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612740/extras/10f1576d9fa296ec5c49eec89034edfb.mp4?t=1599719548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Bokida 的世界观中包含了两个世界：广阔开放，待人探索的光之世界；暗之世界，通向谜之国度的家园。这两个世界在很久之前被相互隔绝，而这很快就会迎来改变。<br>如同恋人分离多年渴望重逢，两个世界很快就会复归一体。作为信使，你的使命则是唤醒光之世界，引导暗之世界，打破那些组织恋人重逢的平衡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612740/extras/0170dd9b6b191023e18a7f407c3c46c6.poster.avif?t=1599719548\" width=616 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612740/extras/0170dd9b6b191023e18a7f407c3c46c6.webm?t=1599719548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612740/extras/0170dd9b6b191023e18a7f407c3c46c6.mp4?t=1599719548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>本作的核心体验建立在游戏中强大的交互工具之上。玩家将通过信使的能力建造色彩斑斓的建筑：精准地切割和雕刻它们，并清除掉残砾。充分发挥自己的创造力，将这个广阔的开放世界向自己希望的模样引导。<br><br>围绕这个充满趣味性的工具进行探索，参与和改造四周的环境。通过增添色彩来给电脑屏幕中的画布带去勃勃生机。起初沉睡的世界会逐渐变成一个美丽的地方。<br>发现壮丽的景观，漫游并潜入另一个世界……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612740/extras/f34dc1005a90bed95adfcc24a7055c87.poster.avif?t=1599719548\" width=616 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612740/extras/f34dc1005a90bed95adfcc24a7055c87.webm?t=1599719548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/612740/extras/f34dc1005a90bed95adfcc24a7055c87.mp4?t=1599719548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
